-- Kennedy Threatened After Brothers Died, Papers Say
-- Justin Blum
-- 2010-06-14T14:02:06Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-14/fbi-s-kennedy-files-show-death-threats-against-late-massachusetts-senator.html

          
          
             The Federal Bureau of Investigation
released a summary of its files on the late Massachusetts
Senator Edward Kennedy.  
 The  files , being released in response to Freedom of
Information Act requests, are to include documents on the
Chappaquiddick incident and on threats directed against Kennedy
and other public figures.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
